channel.title: I have an error I don't know what it is/ causeing my webclient not to work
channel.description:
My webclient worked and now it doesn't, everytime I load it the screen goes white and at the top left hand corner says error, click here for more details so i click and it says run application failed, click for details and I get this:
[URL=http://img28.imageshack.us/i/wtfhz.jpg/][IMG]http://img28.imageshack.us/img28/5354/wtfhz.jpg[/img][/URL]
Help please?, Regards, James

item.title: I have an error I don't know what it is/ causeing my webclient not to work
item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

Well I see two things,

  1. It failed to find the main class
  2. It failed to connect to the site hosting your cache.

Conclusion: On your html page the main class is specified as client.class when it should just be client, and you probably messed up the cache link/it doesn’t exist.
